    Generated pattern matcher API of the org.eclipse.viatra.integration.uml.derivedfeatures.vertexIncoming pattern, providing pattern-specific query methods.

    Use the pattern matcher on a given model via on(ViatraQueryEngine), e.g. in conjunction with ViatraQueryEngine#on(Notifier).

    Matches of the pattern will be represented as VertexIncomingMatch.
